-- ============================================================
-- TEMPLATE 000035 — Per-business seed data
-- Pixie Girl Hub · JBS Praxis · V2.0  (V2.2: service types, perf KPIs)
--
-- Seeds the per-brand defaults so a freshly provisioned schema is
-- immediately functional. Everything seeded here is EDITABLE via
-- the admin UI — these are sensible starting points, not hardcoded
-- constants.
--
-- Seeds:
--   • document_numbering        — per-doc-type sequences (PXG-INV-0001, etc.)
--   • account_groups            — 5 top-level groups
--   • chart_of_accounts         — standard Nigerian retail COA
--   • fiscal_periods            — 12 months for current year + period 13
--   • crm_pipelines + stages    — default sales pipeline
--   • service_types             — V2.2 five-item taxonomy (Faitlyn-relevant)
--   • performance_kpi_definitions — V2.2 weighted KPIs (40/25/20/15)
--   • payroll_deductions        — current Nigerian PAYE / Pension / NHF
--   • stock_locations           — single default warehouse
--   • expense_categories        — 12 starter categories
--   • couriers                  — Chowdeck / GIGL / DHL / Manual starter
--   • email_templates           — 5 starter templates
--   • dashboard_widgets         — 8 starter KPI widgets
--   • report_templates          — V2.2 weekly Sales + Customer reports
--   • Shared tables: also seeds shared.loyalty_tiers for this brand,
--     shared.document_numbering (the sequences live in shared)
-- ============================================================

